---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Aegis AI"
  description="Privacy Policy for Aegis AI — outlining how we collect, use, and protect your personal data in accordance with UAE Personal Data Protection Law (PDPL)."
  canonicalPath="/privacy"
  ogImage="/assets/og-privacy.jpg"
>

<header class="hero-section" style="padding:8rem 0 5rem;">
  <div class="container" style="text-align:center;">
    <nav class="page-breadcrumb" style="justify-content:center; margin-bottom:1.5rem;" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/">Home</a><span>/</span>
      <strong>Privacy Policy</strong>
    </nav>
    <h1>Privacy <span class="gradient-text">Policy</span></h1>
    <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:1.0625rem; max-width:560px; margin:1rem auto 0;">
      Last Updated: May 22, 2026. How we manage and safeguard your data in compliance with UAE Federal Decree-Law No. 45 of 2021 on Personal Data Protection.
    </p>
  </div>
</header>

<main class="section">
  <div class="container" style="max-width:760px;">
    <div class="prose">

      <section>
        <h2>1. Overview</h2>
        <p>At <strong>Aegis AI</strong> ("we", "us", "our"), we respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and share your personal information when you visit our website <strong>https://aegisai.ae</strong>, use our booking system, or engage with our custom AI development, strategy, and team training services in the United Arab Emirates.</p>
        <p>By accessing our site and services, you consent to the processing of your information as described in this policy.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We may collect and process different types of personal data about you, including:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Identity Data:</strong> Full name, job title, and company name.</li>
          <li><strong>Contact Data:</strong> Email address, phone number, and WhatsApp number.</li>
          <li><strong>Business Insights:</strong> Industry, company size, custom AI challenges, budget estimates, and operational notes shared during booking.</li>
          <li><strong>Technical Data:</strong> IP address, browser type, time zone setting, operating system, and details about how you navigate and interact with our website.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
        <p>We only use your personal data for legitimate business purposes as allowed by UAE law, including to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Register you as a new client and process your booking for our Free AI Strategy Consultation.</li>
          <li>Deliver and manage our custom AI models, automation workflows, and tailored training workshops.</li>
          <li>Reach out to you via phone, email, or WhatsApp to schedule calls, send updates, and deliver operational support.</li>
          <li>Optimize and improve our website performance, marketing strategies, and user experience.</li>
          <li>Ensure compliance with legal and regulatory obligations in the UAE.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
        <p>We have implemented robust technical and organizational security measures to prevent your personal data from being accidentally lost, used, accessed, altered, or disclosed in an unauthorized way.</p>
        <p>All information collected through our online contact forms and Booking Modal is transmitted securely via HTTPS encryption. Access to your personal data is strictly restricted to employees, contractors, and partners who have a professional need to know.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>5. Data Sharing and Third-Parties</h2>
        <p>We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal data to third parties. We may share your information with trusted technology partners who assist us in operating our business and hosting our systems (such as Microsoft Azure, OpenAI, Anthropic, Make.com, and n8n), subject to strict confidentiality commitments.</p>
        <p>We may also disclose your personal data if required to do so by UAE law enforcement, court order, or to protect the rights, safety, or security of Aegis AI or our clients.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>6. Your Rights Under UAE Law</h2>
        <p>In accordance with the <strong>UAE Personal Data Protection Law (Federal Decree-Law No. 45 of 2021)</strong>, you have the following rights regarding your personal data:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Right to Access:</strong> You can request details of the personal data we hold about you.</li>
          <li><strong>Right to Correction:</strong> You can request that we update or correct any incomplete or inaccurate data.</li>
          <li><strong>Right to Erasure ("Right to be Forgotten"):</strong> You can request that we delete your personal data under certain conditions.</li>
          <li><strong>Right to Restrict Processing:</strong> You can request that we limit or stop the processing of your data.</li>
          <li><strong>Right to Withdraw Consent:</strong> Where you have given consent for data processing, you can withdraw it at any time.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>To exercise any of these rights, please contact our Data Protection Officer at <strong>hello@aegisai.ae</strong>.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>7. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
        <p>Our website uses standard cookies and logging mechanisms to enhance navigation, analyze site traffic, and deliver personalized user experiences. You can choose to configure your browser to decline cookies, though this may limit your ability to use certain interactive features of our website (such as the multi-step consultation form).</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy, or how your personal information is processed, please reach out to us at:</p>
        <div class="contact-box">
          <p><strong style="color:#00253b;">Aegis AI</strong></p>
          <p>Dubai, United Arab Emirates</p>
          <p><strong>Email:</strong> hello@aegisai.ae</p>
          <p><strong>WhatsApp Support:</strong> +971 4 321 8888</p>
        </div>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</main>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
.prose h2 { font-size: 1.375rem; font-weight: 700; color: #00253b; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,37,59,0.10); padding-bottom: 0.625rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; margin-top: 0; }
    .prose p { color: #42474e; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 0.875rem; }
    .prose ul { color: #42474e; padding-left: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.8; }
    .prose li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .prose strong { color: #111c2d; }
    .prose section { margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
    .contact-box { background: #f0f3ff; border: 1px solid rgba(0,37,59,0.10); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.25rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
    .contact-box p { margin: 0 0 0.375rem; color: #42474e; font-size: 0.9rem; }
</style>